{"tid":41461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡瀾：海南雞全熟似食鞋底","createTime":"2016-12-16T02:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T09:59:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f742e801a5d43efd7af44cdbd002062e0b25e7","tid":41461,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T02:23:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19867066&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19867066%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161216&d=ioH%2FwwjyYnr5BdGcXklXCJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=5c1cd35a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19867066%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161216&h=4dd32a67\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19867066&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161216</a><br />\n<br />\n蔡瀾：海南雞全熟似食鞋底<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n■港人喜食嫩雞，故一般燒味店均不會把白切雞煮太熟。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】測試發現90%活雞樣本含ESBL細菌，消委會建議應徹底煮熟。美味與食物安全似無法並存，食家蔡瀾曾稱海南雞絕不能全熟，否則像吃鞋底。名廚周中亦稱傳統活雞烹調的白切雞要僅熟才夠嫩滑，「外國人食雞先嚡熠熠（音：烚）」。食家劉晉亦指雞八至九成熟最美味，食海南雞要肉色轉白而骨髓呈棗紅最佳。<br />\n<br />\n24個即宰活雞樣本中，有22個驗出ESBL細菌，按建議應徹底煮熟以察安全。但周中偏偏指出，新鮮雞肉鮮味最盛，烹調時只需僅熟，如白切雞用滾水浸熟，咬落肉質才會嫩滑，「啲鬼佬煮雞胸肉至會全熟，係外國人食雞先嚡熠熠」。<br />\n<br />\n周稱新鮮雞即宰即煮，肉裏的乳酸未曾侵蝕肉質，「如果係冰鮮嘅，運輸都起碼一日，會變霉變壞」。不過他指近年禽流感盛行，「好多廚師寧願煮熟啲」，現已難覓正宗僅熟白切雞。<br />\n<br />\n劉晉：骨髓呈棗紅最佳<br />\n<br />\n食家兼留家廚房負責人劉晉表示，雞肉烹調至八至九成熟時味道最好，尤其是不少港人熱愛的海南雞，雞肉只需浸煮至剛變白色，而骨髓呈棗紅為最佳。他稱煮熟與煮得美味是「煮食嘅矛盾」，如西餐不少禽類如鴨或鴿等上碟時都是血紅色，「嗰啲一定好唔衞生㖭」，建議政府部門可制訂指引，如參考美國流行的「危害分析重要管制點（Hazard Analysis and Critical Control Points，HACCP）」，「話畀大家知煮到幾多度可以殺菌，咁就最好啦」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者佘錦洪<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;抗藥菌潛伏腸道　可致敗血症<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;圍堵校委案　李國章驚跌低被踩死　「馮敬恩係主謀，攻擊我」"},{"pid":"688e7a10ff86e9252f6d44b74f7fd1bf2a93899e","tid":41461,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"佢又知鞋底咩味"},{"pid":"a344ba761595465d41fb37ad2f44732e50594f67","tid":41461,"uid":21427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢又知鞋底咩味</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663b18aa9459ae7b8c961785142eeb968f1e387f","tid":41461,"uid":20087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢又知鞋底咩味</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410b08c8063c1e1c52f70afb4688e3d02262c804","tid":41461,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢又知鞋底咩味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae4a3abf886bcd4eef452485062cf3cd947bec6","tid":41461,"uid":2792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"仲有d血既雞真係好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ebca5af0842b5376db7aefe65519770f865ec7","tid":41461,"uid":32462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，而架進化到海南雞飯都有medium rare<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0157df4945be32b63060607f23267aa1c8d6c776","tid":41461,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老味，而架進化到海南雞飯都有medium rare<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374e645599b77dd5a77e0f050b32e0c18cc7c867","tid":41461,"uid":61049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0